---
const { id } = Astro.params;
import '../../../styles/global.css';
---
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Orchestrator - {id}</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-50 font-sans antialiased h-screen flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Monolith Header -->
    <header class="h-14 bg-[#131315] border-b border-[#1c1b1d] flex items-center justify-between px-6 shrink-0">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <h1 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-tighter text-white">COLBY PMO</h1>
            <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 font-mono">{id}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#2a2a2c] rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-white">Healthy</div>
            <a href={`/projects/${id}`} class="text-xs text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Exit Workspace</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-1 flex overflow-hidden bg-[#131315]">
        <!-- Artifact Preview Left Pane -->
        <section class="w-1/2 h-full flex flex-col border-r border-[#1c1b1d] bg-[#1c1b1d]/30">
            <div class="h-12 border-b border-[#1c1b1d] flex items-center justify-between px-4 shrink-0 bg-[#131315]">
                <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Artifact Preview</h2>
                <button class="text-xs text-zinc-400 hover:text-white px-2 py-1 rounded bg-[#201f22]">Copy Markdown</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8">
                <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-headings:font-bold prose-p:text-[#c6c6c6] prose-a:text-white">
                    <h1>System Architecture Overview</h1>
                    <p>This document defines the core structural boundaries of the PMO integration layer. We are utilizing a multi-agent workflow coordinated via Cloudflare Workers.</p>

                    <h2>1. Edge Routing</h2>
                    <p>All traffic enters via the Hono API mounted on the primary Cloudflare Worker.</p>
                    <pre><code class="language-typescript">
import { Hono } from 'hono';
const app = new Hono();
app.get('/health', (c) => c.text('OK'));
                    </code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Jules Assistant Right Pane -->
        <section class="w-1/2 h-full flex flex-col bg-[#131315]">
            <div class="h-12 border-b border-[#1c1b1d] flex items-center px-4 shrink-0">
                <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Jules Assistant</h2>
            </div>

            <!-- Thread Area -->
            <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-6 space-y-6">
                <!-- System Intro -->
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-[#2a2a2c] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-white"><path d="M12 8V4H8"/><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="M2 14h2"/><path d="M20 14h2"/><path d="M15 13v2"/><path d="M9 13v2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 w-full">
                        <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 font-mono uppercase">System</span>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed bg-[#1c1b1d] p-4 rounded-sm">
                            Session initialized. Ready to execute arbitrary modifications against the project repository.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- User Message -->
                <div class="flex gap-4 justify-end">
                    <div class="bg-[#2a2a2c] p-4 rounded-sm text-sm text-white leading-relaxed max-w-[80%] border border-[#353437]">
                        Please review the PRD and generate a Drizzle schema for the new tracking module.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- AI Response with Tool Call -->
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-[#2a2a2c] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-white"><path d="M12 8V4H8"/><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="M2 14h2"/><path d="M20 14h2"/><path d="M15 13v2"/><path d="M9 13v2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 w-full">
                        <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 font-mono uppercase">Jules</span>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed bg-[#1c1b1d] p-4 rounded-sm">
                            I will read the linked PRD and then generate the required schema.
                        </div>

                        <!-- Tool Execution State -->
                        <div class="bg-[#131315] border border-[#1c1b1d] rounded-sm p-3 flex items-center gap-3 w-fit">
                            <svg class="animate-spin text-zinc-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-6.219-8.56"/></svg>
                            <span class="text-xs text-zinc-400 font-mono">Running fetch_document_content...</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Composer Area -->
            <div class="p-6 bg-[#131315] border-t border-[#1c1b1d]">
                <div class="bg-[#1c1b1d] rounded-sm p-2 flex flex-col gap-2 border border-[#2a2a2c] focus-within:border-white/20 transition-colors">
                    <textarea class="w-full bg-transparent text-sm text-white resize-none outline-none p-2 placeholder:text-zinc-600" rows="3" placeholder="Message Jules..."></textarea>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center px-2 pb-1">
                        <button class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m21.44 11.05-9.19 9.19a6 6 0 0 1-8.49-8.49l8.57-8.57A4 4 0 1 1 18 8.84l-8.59 8.57a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l8.49-8.48"/></svg>
                        </button>
                        <button class="bg-white text-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-[2px] text-xs font-bold hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors">
                            Send Message
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center mt-3">
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-zinc-600">AI agents may produce inaccurate code. Verify outputs.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
